title: Tanzania National Archives
text: The Tanzania National Archives (est. 1962) is the <a href="national%20archives">national archives</a> of <a href="Tanzania">Tanzania</a>. The headquarters are located in <a href="Dar%20es%20Salaam">Dar es Salaam</a> on Vijibweni Street in Upanga. Leaders have included J. R. Ede (circa 1960s).
